# Brand Compliance Rules

## Overview
These rules ensure that all code changes, UI updates, and content modifications strictly follow the Lyyli AI brand guidelines.

## Color Compliance

### Primary Colors - STRICT ENFORCEMENT
```typescript
// ALWAYS use these exact color values
const BRAND_COLORS = {
  primary: '#2F5D50',        // Deep professional green
  primaryLight: '#A7D6D1',   // Light accent green
  secondary: '#F7EBEB',      // Soft background
  accent: '#A7D6D1',         // Accent green
  background: '#FFFFFF',     // White background
  foreground: '#2F5D50',     // Dark text
} as const;

// NEVER use these colors
const FORBIDDEN_COLORS = [
  '#000000', '#FF0000', '#00FF00', '#0000FF', // Pure colors
  '#FF6B6B', '#4ECDC4', '#45B7D1', '#96CEB4', // Bright colors
  '#FFEAA7', '#DDA0DD', '#98D8C8', '#F7DC6F'  // Pastel colors
];
```

### Color Usage Rules
- ✅ **Primary green (#2F5D50)** for main CTAs, headers, and brand elements
- ✅ **Light green (#A7D6D1)** for accents, highlights, and secondary actions
- ✅ **Soft background (#F7EBEB)** for section backgrounds and cards
- ❌ **Never use pure colors** (red, blue, yellow) without brand approval
- ❌ **Never use bright or neon colors** that don't match the professional tone

## Typography Compliance

### Font Usage - MANDATORY
```typescript
// ALWAYS use these font families
const TYPOGRAPHY = {
  primary: 'Inter, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif',
  secondary: 'Playfair Display, ui-serif, Georgia, serif',
} as const;

// Font hierarchy - MUST follow this structure
const FONT_HIERARCHY = {
  h1: 'text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold tracking-tight',
  h2: 'text-3xl md:text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight',
  h3: 'text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold',
  h4: 'text-xl md:text-2xl font-medium',
  h5: 'text-lg md:text-xl font-medium',
  h6: 'text-base md:text-lg font-medium',
  body: 'text-base leading-relaxed',
  small: 'text-sm leading-normal',
} as const;
```

### Typography Rules
- ✅ **Inter font** for all body text, buttons, and UI elements
- ✅ **Playfair Display** only for headings and special accents
- ✅ **Consistent hierarchy** - never skip heading levels
- ✅ **Proper line height** - always use leading-relaxed for body text
- ❌ **Never use system fonts** without Inter fallback
- ❌ **Never mix fonts** without clear hierarchy
- ❌ **Never use decorative fonts** without brand approval

## Layout & Spacing Compliance

### Container System - REQUIRED
```typescript
// ALWAYS use this container structure
const LAYOUT = {
  container: 'container mx-auto px-4 py-16',
  maxWidth: 'max-w-6xl mx-auto',
  section: 'py-16 md:py-24',
  grid: 'grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8',
} as const;

// Spacing scale - MUST follow this
const SPACING = {
  xs: '0.25rem',    // 4px
  sm: '0.5rem',     // 8px
  md: '1rem',       // 16px
  lg: '1.5rem',     // 24px
  xl: '2rem',       // 32px
  '2xl': '3rem',    // 48px
  '3xl': '4rem',    // 64px
  '4xl': '6rem',    // 96px
} as const;
```

### Layout Rules
- ✅ **Consistent padding** - always use 2rem (32px) container padding
- ✅ **Responsive design** - mobile-first approach required
- ✅ **Proper spacing** - use the defined spacing scale
- ✅ **Grid system** - use Tailwind's grid classes consistently
- ❌ **Never use arbitrary values** for spacing without approval
- ❌ **Never create layouts** that aren't responsive
- ❌ **Never use fixed widths** that break on mobile

